{"name":"Lake Newt","size":"large","type":"beast","tag":"","alignment":"","hitDice":"7","armorName":"natural armor","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":3,"otherArmorDesc":"15 (natural armor)","speed":"20","burrowSpeed":"20","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"30","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"90 (12d10 + 24)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"15","dexPoints":"12","conPoints":"16","intPoints":"3","wisPoints":"5","chaPoints":"3","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"60","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"2","customCr":"5 (1,800 XP)","customProf":3,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The salamander can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The salamander regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the salamander can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the salamander can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The salamander can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the salamander's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the salamander's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the salamander dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Bite","desc":"_Melee or Ranged Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 11 (2d6 + 4) piercing damage, or 13 (2d8 + 4) piercing damage if used with two hands to make a melee attack, plus 3 (1d6) fire damage."}],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"The newt makes two attacks, one with its bite and one with its tail, but must target different creatures."},{"name":"Bite","desc":"_Melee or Ranged Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft. one target. _Hit:_ [STR 1d6] piercing damage, plus [1D6] cold damage."},{"name":"Tail","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 10 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [STR 1D4] bludgeoning damage. If the tail hits the newt can make another tail attack against an adjacent creature as a bonus action."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[],"skills":[],"damagetypes":[{"name":"cold","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"fire","note":" (Vulnerable)","type":"v"}],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":false,"separationPoint":2,"damage":[]}